## Per-REN overrides

Overrides are per-REN, declared in `ren/REN_<N>/manifest.yaml`. Example:

```yaml
side_effects_overrides:
  - pattern: "CALL PROD_MAESTROBI.DBO.MAIL_ENVIO_*"
    action: redirect_to
    arg: oscar.sirlopu@e2e.pe
    reason: "Need to verify the new email layout for this REN"
```

Overrides only apply for the given REN. The catalog remains unchanged.
